title: WAGO PFC200 Datacenter Signal
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/wago
license: GPL
distribution: kuhn-ruess
description:
 Monitors the configurable status signals exposed by a WAGO PFC200
 datacenter controller via the wioPlcData SNMP table
 (.1.3.6.1.4.1.13576.10.1.100.1.1.3). Each signal carries a description
 (.X.1) and a numeric status code (.X.2). A status code of 1 is treated
 as OK, every other value as CRIT. The description from the device is
 included in the service summary so the controller's fault text (e.g.
 "Notstrom low fuel") becomes visible in Checkmk when a signal trips.

inventory:
 One service per signal index reported by the controller. Indices 1-3
 hold device metadata and are not discovered as services.
